- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with machine learning techniques for natural language processing. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also possible as the paper presents a neural network-based approach. 
- cs.DL (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper deals with deep learning techniques for natural language processing.
